# IMPORTANT

- Always use pnpm to install the dependencies
- When add new shadcn ui components, use pnpm dlx shadcn@latest add <component-name> to add the component to the project.
- To modify, delete or create data in firebase realtime database, use the mutate-data.ts file in the lib/firebase folder.
- All the protected pages present in the src/app/(main)/[role] folder are protected pages and can only be accessed by the authenticated users.
- All the pages present in the src/app/(main) folder are public pages and can be accessed by all the users.

